text: I ordered from pandamart service and the things are awful and will definitely not buy from them anymore. It was a very bad experience, missing items and sending a poor quality item as shown in the pic. The garlic is rotten, and there are worms in it, their food quality control definitely sucks
Received 2 out of 3 expired items and could not receive the $23 refund for it. Will never buy from pandamart and foodpanda anymore. Boycotting the brand now.
One hour to pack my order is just too damn ridiculous.
